name: Princess Style 2.1
description:
I've been sleeping on SD2.1 for too long! There are some FANTASTIC 2.1 models out now, so I feel like it's time for me to port some of my popular TI's over, and wew, do they look good!

This is a Style embedding which turns your image subjects into bonafide Princesses! Think pearls, tiaras, and ballgowns! Simply throw Style-Princess_SD2 on to the end of your prompt (or the start, if the effect doesn't come through strong enough), and bam! - your subject is now a princess - it's as easy as that.

Here's my original 1.5 version.

You can combine this embedding with other embeddings!

Please consider joining my Patreon! Advanced SD tutorials (I show you how I made this!), settings explanations, adult-art, from a female content creator (me!) patreon.com/theally
